      • getBody

        @Nullable
@Nullable java.lang.Object getBody()
        Returns body. There are two types of body.
        • InputStream: if the body's type is input stream, is will be transferred in chunked stream mode.
        • ByteBuffer: if the body's type is byte buffer, is will be transferred in fixed length mode.
        返回:
        body
